{{Quote|Captain, my flight officer reports the launch of three starfighters.|Pong Krell, to [[Clone Captain|Captain]] [[Rex]]|<ref name="Plan of Dissent" />}}
'''Flight officer''' or '''Flight Officer''' was a [[Military rank|rank]] in the [[Galactic Republic]],<ref name="Plan of Dissent" /> [[Galactic Empire]],<ref name="TIE Fighter 1">[[TIE Fighter 1|''TIE Fighter'' 1]]</ref> and the [[Resistance]].<ref name="Expanded Edition" /> The rank was used by the [[Grand Army of the Republic]] during the [[Clone Wars]]. During the [[Battle of Umbara]], a flight [[officer]] reported to [[Jedi General]] [[Pong Krell]] that three [[starfighter]]s had been launched.<ref name="Plan of Dissent" /> [[Imperial Starfighter Pilot|Pilot]] [[Zin Graw]] of the [[204th Imperial Fighter Wing]] held the rank of flight officer.<ref name="TIE Fighter 1">[[TIE Fighter 1|''TIE Fighter'' 1]]</ref> In [[34 ABY]], the rank was held by [[Huetrin Jones]], a member of the Resistance who was stationed at the [[Resistance base]] on [[D'Qar]] during their [[Battle of D'Qar|evacuation]] of the base.<ref name="Expanded Edition" />

